messages:
Name: Fousseni Diabaté
Nationality: Mali
Date of Birth: October 18, 1995
Position: Attacker
Current club: Lausanne-Sport
Super League clubs played for: Lausanne-Sport
Lausanne-Sport's Fousseni Diabaté was not involved in any of the four Super League matches that his club have played so far in 2025/2026.
Diabaté last appeared in a league game on May 24, 2025, playing 89 minutes for Lausanne-Sport versus Servette in a 3-3 draw.
Lausanne-Sport head to Grasshoppers on September 14 the next time the team are in Super League action.
Last season for Lausanne-Sport, Diabaté made 35 Super League appearances, scored seven goals and provided five assists.
Before moving to Lausanne-Sport in September 2023, Diabaté made 32 league appearances in total at Partizan, scoring two goals.
